  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to LXShortcut</title>

    <para>
      The <application>LXShortcut</application> package contains a small
      program used to edit application shortcuts created with
      freedesktop.org Desktop Entry spec.
    </para>

    &lfs75_checked;

